<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śakavaruṣaṁbulu 1309 gunēṁṭi
<lb n="2"/>caitra śukla paurnami sōmavārānanu duttuḍa
<lb n="3"/>prōlōju koḍuku <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g><note n="372-1">The letter A is engraved in smaller characters.</note>Appōju tanakabhīṣṭartasiddhigā
<lb n="4" break="no"/>nu śrīnarasiṁhyanatuniki dhupaAvasaramaṁdu
<lb n="5"/>cātanu Oka doṁḍavanamāla nityamuṁ de
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ci cātiṁpanu būmikūnaya koḍuku
<lb n="7"/>brameku reṁḍu kuṁcālu prasādamu
<lb n="8"/>jōsya varadunāyuni cētanu Enimi
<lb n="9" break="no"/>di maḍalu 8 <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> peṭi ṭavugānu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> I doṁḍava
<lb n="10" break="no"/>namalaku gōpaḷajīyaṁgaricētanu kraya
<lb n="11" break="no"/>mu kona gaṭu 1 pasativāri turppu doṁḍava<unclear>na</unclear>
<lb n="12" break="no"/>māla ṟēpe peṭenu AcaṁdrarkastaIgā peṭaṁga
<lb n="13" break="no"/>laru <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> I dharmmu śrīvaiṣṇava rakṣa śrī
</p>

